WEBVTT

00:03:28.800 --> 00:03:30.360
you have a dangerous mix.

00:03:32.280 --> 00:03:34.080
We see that in political life.

00:03:35.360 --> 00:03:37.216
In part of the world,

00:03:37.240 --> 00:03:39.616
the mix of greed and fear

00:03:39.640 --> 00:03:42.256
means that those who get power

00:03:42.280 --> 00:03:46.720
become reluctant to give it back.

00:03:48.920 --> 00:03:50.456
One of the many things

00:03:50.480 --> 00:03:55.216
I like and admire in our democracies

00:03:55.240 --> 00:03:57.056
are the norms

00:03:57.080 --> 00:04:00.256
that make our leaders hand over power